cs.AR, cs.ET, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SY

This paper discusses the challenges and methodologies of restructuring software code for HLS tools, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR) and electronic design automation (cs.ET). The paper also discusses the need for a hardware programming model for software programmers, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper focuses on enabling FPGAs for a broader set of programmers, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
